search "user" for all customized configs

<ctrl+m> -> go to symbol in workspace, used to search definition (ctrl + T), remove <ctrl + M> in vim to avoid conflict
<ctrl+u> -> go to symbol in editor <ctrl + shift + o>
<ctrl+o> -> go backward <ctrl + alt + ->
<ctrl+i> -> go forward <ctrl + shift + ->
<ctrl+h> -> show explorer (switch between explorer and main window)
<ctrl+f> -> view: toggle primary side bar visibility
<ctrl+j> -> toggle terminal (ctrl + `)
<alt+v>  -> View: Split Editor Down
<alt+h>  -> View: Split Editor
